// >>>>> To Create a react APP with Vite:

> npm create vite@latest  // or vite@4.1.0 for exact version
> Project name: <name it like you want to>
> Select a framework: React
> Select a language: TypeScript

// Lets' install all libraries
> cd react-app
> npm i
> code .                  // Opens VS Code

// At VS Code you can open Terminate with Ctrl + `
// To run a webserver

> npm run dev             // http://localhost:5173

// Extension of TypeScript files are .ts (for plain TS files) or .tsx (for TS components)

// >>>>> 
